{
  "stem": "2226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So some even broke the-- broke the floor for the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if they catch you, the Poles give you away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't have to go over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If that would be the case, you could, I wouldn't say, much-- maybe another 20% will be alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see-- you know, Judy what happened in Kielce, the pogrom right after the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The trip?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two nights and three days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Evening.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Saturday evening.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember, evening.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The date when I left, I think, the 7th-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] I think it would have been the 7th or the 9th of December, '42.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, right away we had a doctor with us-- he took the poison, the pill.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He poisoned himself right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He saw there-- we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't-- they fooled us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said-- they said that they take us to work, like the parents and the-- the children are going to stay in the houses and the barracks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were going to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we come home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So right away, as soon as they opened the barracks-- the-- the cattle wagons-- so there's pictures in the book.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They opened the cattle wagons, started with the-- the sticks hitting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you would never believe it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They killed right away on this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So who knows?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we stayed-- I remember like that with the same men who was in the city how we select a first transport.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A guy was in the transport [INAUDIBLE] people, 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So 1,000 people, you need only 10-- 10-- 10-- 10-- 10 cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So for the 1,000 people-- then they put in another 500 second transport for another city.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
